<description>
    <short>
        <en>Enables you to configure SAML with an external IdP to authenticate and authorize users using the GLPI UI.</en>
    </short>
    <long>
        <en>Glpisaml provides SAML Single Sign On (SSO) capabilties for GLPI. Glpisaml is written with GLPI10+ 
            support in mind. It uses GLPI core components and best-practices for maximum compatibility and 
            maintainability. The plugin enables you to configure multiple SAML providers allowing your customers
            SSO access as well. The plugin will create new GLPI users on the fly and apply jit rules to assign 
            entities, groups and profiles. For questions join our discord at: https://discord.gg/KyMdkqJcGz. 
            Find an issue, register it at my codeberg site. Written with passion for OSS, Enjoy!
        </en>
    </long>
</description>
